0.title: Aggregate block storage available

timeseries block_storage_available = avg(netapp.ontap.aggregate.block_storage_available), by: { `dt.entity.netapp_ontap:aggregate` }
| fieldsAdd entityName(`dt.entity.netapp_ontap:aggregate`)
| sort arrayAvg(block_storage_available) desc
| limit 20
